data.description: This end unit townhome in the Villa Rosa neighborhood offers stunning mountain views, a one car attached garage, and is in close proximity to trails, parks, dining, and shopping!  This home has been well cared for and is move-in ready. Located just moments from the I-25, shopping centers, and great schools, this location offers unbeatable convenience. Step outside and enjoy the maintenance free landscaping and private deck, where you can relax and take in the breathtaking views. Inside, you'll find double master suites, each with their own bath. One of the master suites also features its own private deck with stunning views.  If you're looking for a peaceful and serene retreat in the Westside area, look no further than this Villa Rosa townhome. Contact us today to schedule a showing and experience the beauty and convenience of this beautiful townhome!
